{"tid":755441,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由小學至中學都冇寫過簡體字？","createTime":"2018-07-25T08:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T04:01:12.000Z","uid":146917,"like":162,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5f6d2ed424112d7ba3412f7ac4c82f3e147d13","tid":755441,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"包括係考試 但唔包括 普通話堂 and 普通話考試<br />\n一句講曬有就有冇就冇，唔好話有但乜乜乜咁多藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先 冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前中學老師係中文堂貪方便有d字寫簡體字話快d<br />\n然後我轉返佢做繁體但又唔記得左點寫，問隔離又話我都跟老師寫左簡體，屌 搞到我用手機google隻字繁體點寫，最後比人收撚埋部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 一繁一簡覺得好撚on9 好唔撚夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1d587e675200eac18df3a482f142b9284a1273","tid":755441,"uid":76622,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"老師教書時會喺黑板寫, 會快啲<br />\n但從來都無教, 我亦無自學, 一直只識睇"},{"pid":"8fa4ebf5512ab23fd7226efd34441fb0a2c96527","tid":755441,"uid":82879,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:19:11.000Z","msg":"人生至今都未寫過"},{"pid":"f02d4c3d4b60bbcb8996f11d9dae139d3f3961ca","tid":755441,"uid":11336,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"我讀文學同中史都堅持寫正體字<br />\n一來唔識殘體 二來覺得好撚柒"},{"pid":"96f1b8f296773136364fdc90fc7c33da897845bf","tid":755441,"uid":146917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1c1d587e675200eac18df3a482f142b9284a1273","tid":755441,"uid":76622,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"老師教書時會喺黑板寫, 會快啲<br />\n但從來都無教, 我亦無自學, 一直只識睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"我都係 識睇唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d846ba3aa924ef8d79655294bbdd18b65fce4a3","tid":755441,"uid":70027,"like":0,"disl